Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.66,0:06:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28\1c&HB74422&}片名： 人格面具 (假面)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.60,0:06:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\1c&HA94526&\b1}导演：英格玛．伯格曼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.89,0:06:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\1c&HA94526&\b1}主演：比比．安德森
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.80,0:06:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\1c&HA94526&\b1}主演：莉芙．厄尔曼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.02,0:07:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你找我吗？医生\NYou wanted to talk with me, doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.36,0:07:12.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你见过沃哥夫人了吗，艾玛护士？\NHave you been to see Mrs. Vogler yet, Sister Alma?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.93,0:07:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没，现在还没有\NNo, not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.10,0:07:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我给你解释一下她的情况\NLet me explain her situation
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.30,0:07:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以及为什么让你来照顾她的原因\Nand the reason why you have been hired to care for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.97,0:07:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正如你知道的，沃哥夫人是一名演员\NMrs. Vogler is an actress, as you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.71,0:07:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在她的最后一场演出《恋父》中\NDuring her last performance of Electra,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.44,0:07:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她突然就不说话了，并很惊讶地看周围的情况\Nshe fell silent and looked around as if in surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.68,0:07:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她这样沉默了一分多钟\NShe was silent for over a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.50,0:07:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之后她道歉了，并说她很想笑\NShe apologized afterward, saying she had got the urge to laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.87,0:07:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第二天剧院上班的时候\NThe next day the theater rang,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.17,0:07:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沃哥夫人没有赶去排演\Nas Mrs. Vogler had not come to rehearsals.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.34,0:08:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仆人发现她仍然躺在床上\NThe maid found her still in bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.84,0:08:05.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她已经醒了，但不搭理女仆也不动\NShe was awake but did not talk or move.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.48,0:08:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这种情况到目前为止已经有三个月了\NThis condition has now lasted for three months.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.32,0:08:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她已经做了各种检查\NShe has had all sorts of tests.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.35,0:08:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,心智上和身体上都很正常\NShe's healthy both mentally and physically.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.96,0:08:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚至没有一点异常反应\NIt's not even some kind of hysterical reaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.70,0:08:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什么疑问吗，艾玛护士？\NAny questions, Sister Alma?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.93,0:08:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那好，你可以去沃哥夫人那里了\NWell, then, you can go to Mrs. Vogler now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.58,0:08:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好，沃哥夫人\NHow do you do, Mrs. Vogler?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.15,0:08:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是艾玛护士\NI am Sister Alma.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.22,0:08:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是来照顾你的\NI'm here to take care of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.29,0:08:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或许我该向你介绍一下我自己\NMaybe I should tell you a little about myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.89,0:08:53.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我今年25岁，已经订婚了\NI'm 25 years old and engaged.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.96,0:08:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,两年前取得护士资格征\NI graduated from nursing school two years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.17,0:09:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我父母在乡下有一个农场\NMy parents have a farm in the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.34,0:09:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我母亲在结婚之前也是个护士\NMy mother was also a nurse until she got married.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.51,0:09:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我该为你拿晚餐了\NI should go get your dinner tray.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.58,0:09:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,炸猪肝和水果色拉\NFried liver and fruit salad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.58,0:09:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看起来很美味\NIt looked tasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.41,0:09:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要加个枕头吗？这样行吗？\NAnother pillow? Is that good?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.96,0:09:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾玛护士，你的第一印象如何？\NSister Alma, what's your first impression?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.33,0:09:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知该怎么说，医生\NI don't know what to say, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.40,0:09:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她的脸看起来很温和，还带点孩子气\NHer face looks soft, almost childish.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.90,0:09:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但她的眼神……\NThen you see her eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.97,0:09:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有种让人不舒服的表情\NShe has a mean look, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.21,0:09:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道．我不应该……  你想说什么？\N- I don't know. I shouldn't... - What were you going to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.81,0:09:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在想是否该负责照顾这个病人\NI thought I should say no to this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.22,0:09:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？害怕了？\NWhy? Did something frighten you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.95,0:09:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，没有\NNo, not exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.35,0:09:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能沃哥夫人需要更年长的人\NPerhaps Mrs. Vogler needs an older person
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.06,0:09:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,生活经验更丰富的\Nwith more life experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.33,0:10:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可能应付不了她……  应付？在什么方面？\N- I might not be able to handle her. - Handle? In what way?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.56,0:10:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,精神方面  精神方面？\N- Mentally. - Mentally?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.63,0:10:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果沃哥夫人的沉默和呆滞不是因为身体缘故……\NIf Mrs. Vogler's silence and immobility are her decision...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.11,0:10:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎样？\NWell?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.57,0:10:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那显示了她很强的精神力量\NThat shows great mental strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.31,0:10:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可能应付不了\NI might not be able to cope.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.35,0:10:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我猜你青定想看看日落\NI thought that you might want to see the sunset.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.02,0:10:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要我打开收音机吗？\NShall I turn on the radio?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.16,0:10:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想今晚有场歌剧\NThere is a play.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.36,0:10:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起，亲爱的\NI'm sorry, my love.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.43,0:10:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噢，你得原谅我\NOh, you have to forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.50,0:10:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我什么都不要，但求你的原谅\NI want nothing but your forgiveness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.07,0:10:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原谅我，我能……\NForgive me and I can...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.64,0:10:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在笑什么，沃哥夫人？这女演员很好笑吗？\NWhat are you laughing at, Mrs. Vogler? Is the actress so funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.55,0:10:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你懂什么是宽恕吗？你知道什么？\NWhat do you know about mercy? What do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.18,0:10:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道什么是宽恕？\NWhat do you know about mercy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.56,0:11:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沃哥夫人，我不理解这些东西\NMrs. Vogler, I don't understand those things.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.40,0:11:12.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我对电影和戏剧很感兴趣，但我不经常去\NI'm interested in film and theater, but I don't go very often.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.33,0:11:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很欣赏艺术家\NI have a tremendous admiration for artists.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.10,0:11:21.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我认为艺术对人们的生活是很重要的\NI think that art is of enormous importance in people's lives,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.24,0:11:24.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尤其是对那些有困扰的人来说\Nespecially for those who have problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.68,0:11:28.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不应该对你讲这些的，沃哥夫人\NI shouldn't talk about these things with you, Mrs. Vogler.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.78,0:11:31.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是在履薄冰\NI'm skating on thin ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.85,0:11:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看看有什么音乐没\NLet's see if there's some music.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.52,0:11:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个行吗？\NIs that all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.96,0:11:42.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚安，沃哥夫人，做个好梦！\NGood night, then, Mrs. Vogler. Sleep well!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.67,0:13:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该死\NDamn...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.35,0:13:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真滑稽\NIt's funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.75,0:13:49.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以随心所欲…\NYou can go about as you please...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.09,0:13:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做任何事\N...do almost anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.36,0:13:57.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要嫁给卡尔．亨利克，生几个孩子\NI'll marry Karl-Henrik and have a couple of children,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.93,0:13:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都由我来养\Nwhich I'll have to raise.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.17,0:14:04.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一切都是注定的，在我内心里面\NAll of this is predestined. It's inside me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.07,0:14:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没什么可担心的\NIt's nothing to think about.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.57,0:14:10.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是一种很安全的感觉\NIt's a safe feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.04,0:14:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有一份喜欢的工作\NI have a job that I like and enjoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.38,0:14:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,足矣…\NThat's good, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.12,0:14:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但另一方面…\N...but in another way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.99,0:14:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也还不错\NBut it's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.26,0:14:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还行\NGood.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.67,0:14:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞不懂她到底是怎么回事\NI wonder what's really wrong with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.68,0:14:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊丽莎白．沃哥\NElisabet Vogler.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.75,0:14:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊丽莎白\NElisabet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.37,0:14:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在越南南部出现的骇人听闻的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.37,0:14:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,整个广场刹那间聚集了许多人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.38,0:15:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天刚好也是当地的重大节日
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.38,0:15:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有的警察很快就赶到现场
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.39,0:15:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是这里有史以来的第一桩事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.40,0:15:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,双方的斗争很激烈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.40,0:15:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其中有131人受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.41,0:15:41.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其中一名和尚自焚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.41,0:15:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,火势很盛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.41,0:15:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警察没能把他抢救出来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.42,0:16:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,此人自焚的真正目的还不明确
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.28,0:16:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沃哥夫人，要我给你打开信吗？\NMrs. Vogler, would you like me to open the letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.15,0:16:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要我读给你听吗？\NShall I read it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.83,0:16:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要我读给你听吗？\NShall I read it to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.51,0:16:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“亲爱的伊丽莎白\N"Dearest Elisabet,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.67,0:17:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,”因为他们不让我探望你，所以只能给你写信了\N"Since I'm not allowed to see you, I'm writing to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.24,0:17:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“你也可以不看我的信，扔掉它\NYou don't have to read my letter. You can ignore it."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.02,0:17:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,”我禁不住想用这种方式跟你联系\N"I cannot help seeking contact with you this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.92,0:17:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“我被众多问题困扰着…\N"I'm haunted by a constant question...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.49,0:17:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“我是不是在某些方面伤害了你？\N"Have I hurt you in any way?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.16,0:17:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“是不是在不知不觉中伤害了你？\NHave I unknowingly hurt you?"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.03,0:17:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“我们之间是不是有很大的误会？”\N"Is there some terrible misunderstanding between us?"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.08,0:17:33.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真的想让我再念下去吗？\NDo you really want me to go on?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.99,0:17:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“就我所知现在我们还是幸福的\N"I thought we were happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.22,0:17:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“我们从未如此亲近\NWe have never been so close."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.50,0:17:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“还记得你说过\N"Do you remember saying,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.30,0:17:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“我开始知道婚姻意味着什么吗？\N"'I'm beginning to understand what it means to be married'?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.00,0:18:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“你曾经告诉过我…\N'You have taught me..."'
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.87,0:18:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看不清这个\NI can't read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.71,0:18:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“你曾经告诉过我…\N"'You have taught..."'
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.44,0:18:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噢，知道了\NNow I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.18,0:18:11.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“你曾经告诉过我，我们之间的交往\N"'You have taught me that we have to see each other
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.41,0:18:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“要像两个天真的孩子一样\N"'as two anxious children,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.65,0:18:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“用善意和最好的动机\N"'filled with good will and the best intentions,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.39,0:18:21.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“但…\Nbut ru..."'
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.16,0:18:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了\NNow I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.36,0:18:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“但却被我们只能部分控制的力量统治了\N"'... ruled by powers that we can only partially control.'
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.43,0:18:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“你还记得你曾经说过的这些吗？\NDo you remember saying all that?"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.44,0:18:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“我们到森林里漫步\N"We went for a walk in the woods,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.34,0:18:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“你停下来，抓着我外套的腰带\Nand you stopped and grabbed the belt of my coat."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.98,0:18:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,信里面有张照片\NThere is a photo with the letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.82,0:18:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你儿子的照片，我不知道是否…\NA photo of your son. I don't know if...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.49,0:18:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要看吗，沃哥夫人？\NDo you want it, Mrs. Vogler?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.66,0:19:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他看起来真可爱\NHe looks terribly cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.13,0:19:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊丽莎白，我不知道\NElisabet, I don't think there's any point
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.20,0:19:38.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你呆在这医院里有什么意义\Nin your staying at the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.80,0:19:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这里你只会受到伤害\NIt's just hurting you to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.97,0:19:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然你不想回家，我建议你和艾玛护士\NSince you don't want to go home, I suggest you and Sister Alma
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.64,0:19:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去我海边的夏日小屋住段日子\Nstay at my summer house by the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.65,0:19:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以为我不明白吗？\NDon't you think I understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.55,0:19:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无望的恶梦，不是表面上的，而是本质上的\NThe hopeless dream of being. Not seeming, but being.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.99,0:20:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每个梦醒时分都在时刻警惕\NIn every waking moment aware, alert.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.16,0:20:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,两者之间的战争…别人怎么看你和你究竟是谁\NThe tug of war... what you are with others and who you really are.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.67,0:20:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一种眩晕的感觉\NA feeling of vertigo
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.23,0:20:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一种想被最终暴露的持久的渴望\Nand a constant hunger to be finally exposed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.51,0:20:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望被看透，被击倒…\NTo be seen through, cut down...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.68,0:20:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚至被淹没\Neven obliterated.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.35,0:20:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每个欺骗的谚语，每个虚假的表情\NEvery tone of voice a lie. Every gesture false.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.75,0:20:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每次苦涩的微笑\NEvery smile a grimace.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.95,0:20:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自杀？\NCommit suicide?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.86,0:20:38.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是不可思议的\NThat's unthinkable.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.63,0:20:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不会那样做\NYou don't do things like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.86,0:20:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是你可以沉默和静坐\NBut you can refuse to move and be silent.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.43,0:20:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样，你至少不用撒谎\NThen, at least, you're not lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.70,0:20:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以把自己封闭起来，把世界关在门外\NYou can shut yourself in, shut out the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.11,0:20:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样你无需扮演任何角色\NThen you don't have to play any roles,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.17,0:20:55.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做任何虚伪的表情和手势\Nshow any faces, make false gestures.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.58,0:20:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是这么想的…\NYou'd think so...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.48,0:21:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但现实是残酷的\N...but reality is diabolical.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.75,0:21:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的藏身之所也并非是密不透风的\NYour hiding-place isn't watertight.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.82,0:21:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到处都充斥着生活的骗局\NLife trickles in everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.16,0:21:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不得不做出反应\NYou're forced to react.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.50,0:21:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没人在乎\NNobody asks if it's real or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.67,0:21:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是说实话还是撒谎\Nif you're honest or a liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.57,0:21:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是只在剧院里才变得重要的事\NThat's only important at the theater,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.64,0:21:24.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或者甚至在那里也不是\Nperhaps not even there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.18,0:21:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊丽莎白，我懂你为何要沉默，为何不动弹\NElisabet, I understand why you're silent, why you don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.18,0:21:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的毫无生气已成定局\NYour lifelessness has become a fantastic part.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.85,0:21:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能理解，而且很钦佩\NI understand and I admire you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.69,0:21:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想你该在这件事平静之后再扮演这个角色\NI think you should play this part until it's done...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.53,0:21:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直到人们不再感兴趣\N...until it's no longer interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.76,0:21:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你便可摆脱了\NThen you can leave it,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.37,0:21:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像你摆脱其它角色一样\Nas you leave all your roles.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.84,0:22:01.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沃哥夫人和艾玛护士\NMrs. Vogler and Sister Alma
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.71,0:22:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搬到了医生的夏日小屋\Nmove into the doctor's summer house.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.71,0:22:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这位演员很喜欢这里的海滩\NThe seaside stay agrees very well with the actress.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.22,0:22:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,漫步，钓鱼，烹饪，写信，娱乐\NHer former apathy gives way to long walks, fishing,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.52,0:22:17.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,使她先前的冷漠逐渐消逝\Ncooking, letter-writing, and other diversions.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.53,0:22:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾玛护士也非常喜欢这里的乡村生活\NSister Alma enjoys the seclusion of the countryside
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.56,0:22:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,并且很细心的照顾着她的病人\Nand takes great care of her patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.91,0:23:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟人比手会倒霉的\NIt's bad luck to compare hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.83,0:23:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊丽莎白，我给你读一段书好吗？\NElisabet, can I read a bit of my book to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.73,0:23:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是不打扰你的话？听听这个…\NOr am I disturbing you? Listen to this...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.14,0:23:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“正如我们知道，自身固有的焦虑\N"The anxiety we carry with us,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.24,0:23:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“我们所有破碎的梦，莫名的残忍\N"all our broken dreams, the inexplicable cruelty,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.61,0:23:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“对死亡的恐惧\N"the fear of death,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.88,0:23:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“以及对俗世痛苦深刻的洞察\Nthe painful insight into our earthly condition..."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.62,0:23:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“已经破灭了我们超凡脱俗的希望\N"...have worn out our hope of a divine salvation.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.29,0:23:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“我们内心抵抗黑暗和沉默的\N"The cries of our faith and doubt
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.29,0:24:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“信仰和疑虑的呼声\N"against the darkness and the silence
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.46,0:24:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“是我们孤独和恐惧\N"are terrible proof
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.33,0:24:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“最好的证明”\Nof our loneliness and fear."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.00,0:24:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得是这样吗？\NDo you think it's like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.14,0:24:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不相信\NI don't believe that.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.31,0:24:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想改变…但是我太懒了\NTo change... but I'm so lazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.42,0:24:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这让我很内疚\NAnd it makes me feel guilty.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.49,0:24:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡尔．亨利克经常指责我没有抱负\NKarl-Henrik always scolds me for not having any ambitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.22,0:24:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他说我像具僵尸\NHe says I'm like a zombie.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.63,0:24:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得这不公平\NI think it's unfair.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.69,0:24:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我半业时是班上的好学生\NI graduated with the highest marks in my class.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.00,0:24:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能他说的是别的方面吧\NMaybe he means something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.34,0:24:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你？\NYou?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.90,0:24:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉\NI'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.97,0:24:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道…\NYou know...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.31,0:24:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我毕业的那所医院\NAt the hospital, where I graduated,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.51,0:24:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有个专门给老护士住的地方\Nthere is a home for old nurses,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.08,0:24:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些一辈子都做护士的人…\Nones who've been nurses all of their lives and lived for their work...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.52,0:24:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成天穿着白大褂…\Nalways in uniform...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.25,0:25:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她们住在那里\Nand they live there.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.15,0:25:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想象一下一种能让你投入一生的强烈召唤…\NImagine having a calling that strong\Nthat you devote your life to it...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.52,0:25:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相信一件事情并去做\NBelieving in something, doing something.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.60,0:25:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,认为你的生命因之而有意义\NTo think your life has meaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.37,0:25:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢这样\NI like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.87,0:25:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无论怎样都坚持下去\NSticking to it whatever happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.94,0:25:21.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样你对别人来说是很重要的\NI think you should be of importance to others.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.71,0:25:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你相信吗？\NDo you believe that?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.85,0:25:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道这听起来很幼稚，但我相信这个
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.55,0:25:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好大的雨！\NWhat a downpour!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.39,0:25:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，他结婚了\NYes, he was married.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.99,0:25:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们已经恋爱了五年\NWe had an affair for five years.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.56,0:25:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之后，他自然厌倦了\NThen he got tired, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.57,0:25:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是如此的爱他，他是我的初恋\NI was so in love, and he was the first.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.57,0:25:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像一种持续的痛苦…\NIt was like a prolonged pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.34,0:25:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,长期的隐痛，及短期的…\N...long periods of pain and short moments of...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.01,0:26:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想起这些都是因为你教我吸烟的缘故\NI started thinking about it all because you've taught me to smoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.25,0:26:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他吸烟很厉害\NHe smoked a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.09,0:26:08.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,后来想想，这当然是很陈腐的，就像低级小说一样\NIn hindsight, it's banal, of course. Sort of like pulp fiction.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.69,0:26:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听起来很怪但我觉得一切好象虚幻\NIn a strange way, it was never real.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.20,0:26:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道该怎么形容\NI don't know how to describe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.10,0:26:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对他来讲我虚幻的\NI was never real to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.27,0:26:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但可以青定的是我的痛苦是真实的\NBut my pain was real, that's for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.81,0:26:33.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从某方面说，那是它的一部分，从某个令人呕心的方面\NIn some way, that was a part of it, in some nauseating way,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.21,0:26:35.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像应该是这样的一样\Nas if it should be like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.88,0:26:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚至我们对彼此所说的一切\NEven the things we said to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.43,0:26:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人们说我是一个很好的倾听者\NPeople tell me that I'm a good listener.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.83,0:26:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好笑是吧？\NIsn't that strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.90,0:26:55.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从没有人倾听过我说话，像你这样\NNobody ever bothered to listen to me. Not the way you do now.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.64,0:26:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你倾听\NYou listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.70,0:27:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想你是第一个听我说话的人\NI think you're the first person to listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.77,0:27:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定很无趣，你可以看你的书\NIt can't be interesting. You could read a book instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.51,0:27:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看着我，聊天，我希望这不会激怒你\NLook at me, talking. I hope it doesn't irritate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.72,0:27:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聊天的感觉真好，是如此温暖和美妙\NIt feels so good to talk. It feels warm and nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.79,0:27:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以前从没有过这种感觉\NI've never been in a mood like this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.46,0:27:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都想有个姐妹，我只有哥哥\NI've always wanted a sister. I only have brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.03,0:27:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,七个，很奇怪，是不是？然后我就出生了\NSeven of them. Strange, eh? And then I turned up.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.47,0:27:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打从记事时起，就记得身边全是男孩\NBoys have surrounded me all my life, as long as I can remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.80,0:27:33.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我喜欢男孩\NBut I like boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.31,0:27:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但作为一个演员我想你一定了解\NBut you would know that with your experience as an actress.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.81,0:27:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我那么喜欢卡尔．亨利克，但是…\NI like Karl-Henrik so much, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.15,0:27:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你或许只会爱一次\NYou probably only love once.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.05,0:27:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我对他那么忠诚\NI'm faithful to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.29,0:27:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然因为我的职业，我也没有不忠的机会\NThere are opportunities in my profession, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.49,0:27:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡尔．亨利克和我曾在海边租了一个小别墅\NKarl-Henrik and I had rented a cottage by the sea once.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.16,0:28:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是六月份，就我们两个\NIt was in June, and we were all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.00,0:28:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一天卡尔．亨利克去镇上了\NOne day Karl-Henrik had gone into town.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.34,0:28:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一个人去了海滩\NI went to the beach on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.87,0:28:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那天天气晴朗暖和\NIt was a warm and nice day.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.51,0:28:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有个女孩躺在那儿\NThere was another girl there.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.08,0:28:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她从另一个岛来\NShe had come from another island
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.15,0:28:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢我们这海滩的光线充足和隐蔽\Nbecause our beach was sunnier and more secluded.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.46,0:28:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们全裸着躺在那晒日光浴…\NWe lay there completely naked and sunbathed...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.63,0:28:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,涂防晒霜，休憩\N...dozing off and on, putting sunscreen on.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.97,0:28:36.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们戴着廉价草帽\NWe had silly straw hats on.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.14,0:28:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的上面缠有一条蓝色的丝巾\NMine had a blue ribbon.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.48,0:28:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我躺在那里…\NI lay there...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.88,0:28:51.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看着周围的环境，享受大海和阳光\NIooking out at the landscape, at the sea and the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.28,0:28:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,确实很有趣\NIt was kind of funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.99,0:29:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,突然我看到上面岩石上有两个身影\NSuddenly I saw two figures on the rocks above us.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.33,0:29:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们躲在背后时不时地偷看一下\NThey hid and peeped out occasionally.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.33,0:29:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我对那女孩说：“有两个男孩在偷看我们”\N"Two boys are looking at us," I said to the girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.24,0:29:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那女孩叫卡特拉\NHer name was Katarina.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.41,0:29:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“让他们看好了”，她说，并翻过身来\N"Let them look," she said, and turned over on her back.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.75,0:29:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我当时感觉很滑稽\NI had a funny feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.82,0:29:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想跳起来，穿好衣服\NI wanted to jump up and put my suit on,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.22,0:29:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我仍然俯卧在那里\Nbut I just lay there on my stomach with my bottom in the air,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.46,0:29:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常冷静，一点都不觉尴尬\Nunembarrassed, totally calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.80,0:29:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且卡特拉就在我的旁边\NAnd Katarina was next to me
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.77,0:29:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大腿和乳房都露在外面\Nwith her breasts and big thighs.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.27,0:29:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她只是不断的傻笑\NShe was just giggling.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.98,0:29:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我注意到男孩们正在向我们走近\NI noticed that the boys were coming closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.21,0:29:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们就站在那里看着我们\NThey just stood there looking at us.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.25,0:29:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看出他们的怯懦\NI noticed they were very young.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.42,0:30:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个大胆点的开始接近我们…\NThe boldest one approached us...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.16,0:30:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,并蹲在卡特拉的旁边\N...and squatted down next to Katarina.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.66,0:30:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他假装是在扳他的脚趾\NHe pretended to be busy picking his toes.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.00,0:30:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我感觉非常奇怪\NI felt very strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.51,0:30:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,突然，卡特拉对他说\NSuddenly Katarina said to him,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.68,0:30:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“嗨，你，怎么不过来？”\N"Hey, you, why don't you come over here?"
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.01,0:30:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后她拉着他的手帮他把裤子和衬衫脱下来\NThen she took his hand and helped him take off his jeans and shirt
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.08,0:30:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,突然他就骑到她的身上\NSuddenly he was on top of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.82,0:30:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她指引着他，抓着他的屁股\NShe guided him in and held his butt.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.86,0:30:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,另一个男孩就坐着看\NThe other boy just sat and watched.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.20,0:30:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我听到卡特拉笑着和那男孩耳语\NI heard Katarina whisper in the boy's ear and laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.20,0:30:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的脸就对着我的脸\NHis face was right next to mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.04,0:30:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是一张红彤彤的胖脸\NIt was red and swollen.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.51,0:31:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,突然我转过去，对他们说\NSuddenly I turned and said,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.91,0:31:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“能不能也到我这来？”\N"Aren't you coming to me, too?"
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.42,0:31:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡特拉说：“去她那吧”\NAnd Katarina said, "Go to her now."
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.42,0:31:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他便从她身上下来\NHe pulled out of her and...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.16,0:31:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后骑到我身上，很粗鲁\Nthen fell on top of me, completely hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.06,0:31:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他抓着我的乳房\NHe grabbed my breast.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.13,0:31:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那很痛！\NIt hurt so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.90,0:31:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很快便就被征服了，并马上兴奋起来\NI was overwhelmed and came almost immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.11,0:31:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你能相信吗？\NCan you believe it?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.51,0:31:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想告诉他小心点，别让我怀孕了…\NI wanted to tell him to be careful not to make me pregnant...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.18,0:31:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他高潮来临时…\N...when he came.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.74,0:31:38.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有一种从未有过的体验…\NI felt something I'd never felt in my life...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.12,0:31:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他把精液于射入我的体内\Nhow his sperm was shooting inside me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.19,0:31:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他抓着我的肩膀向后仰\NHe held my shoulders and bent backwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.36,0:31:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我来了一次又一次\NI came over and over.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.03,0:31:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡特拉躺在那里看着，从后面抱住他\NKatarina lay there watching and held him from behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.37,0:32:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完事后，她就抱着他\NAfter he came, she took him in her arms
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.14,0:32:05.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用他的手来自慰\Nand used his hand to make herself come.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.11,0:32:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快到高潮时，她就叫得像个女妖\NWhen she came, she screamed like a banshee.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.15,0:32:18.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们三个都开始笑\NThe three of us started laughing.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.49,0:32:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们又叫了那个还在斜坡上的男孩\NWe called to the other boy, who was sitting on the slope.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.16,0:32:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他叫彼得\NHis name was Peter.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.33,0:32:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在阳光下颤抖而且看起来挺不解\NHe seemed confused and was shivering there in the sunshine.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.17,0:32:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡特拉开了他的裤子和他玩\NKatarina unbuttoned his pants and started to play with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.51,0:32:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他快射时，她就把它放在她嘴里\NAnd when he came, she took him in her mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.02,0:32:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他弯下身去，吻她的背\NHe bent down and kissed her back.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.52,0:32:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她转过身去，用双手抱住他的头\NShe turned around, took his head in both hands,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.52,0:32:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把她的乳房给他\Nand gave him her breast.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.09,0:32:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,另一个男孩非常兴奋，我们又开始了\NThe other boy got so excited that he and I started all over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.18,0:33:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还和前一次一样美妙\NIt was just as nice as before.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.19,0:33:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后我们一起游泳，之后就分道扬镳了\NThen we had a swim and went our separate ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.27,0:33:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回到家时，卡尔．亨利克已经从镇上回来了\NWhen I came home, Karl-Henrik was already back from town.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.04,0:33:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们共进晚餐并喝了点红酒\NWe had dinner and some red wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.15,0:33:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后我们开始做爱\NThen we had sex.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.15,0:33:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感觉从未没那么好过，以前或后来\NIt had never been that good, before or after.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.32,0:33:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你能理解吗？\NCan you understand that?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.20,0:33:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然我怀孕了\NAnd I got pregnant, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.33,0:33:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡尔．亨利克是一个医生\NKarl-Henrik, studying to be a doctor,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.56,0:33:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,带我去一个同事那里堕了胎\Ntook me to a colleague who carried out the abortion.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.97,0:33:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们无所谓因为我们不想要孩子\NWe were both pleased. We didn't want to have children.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.21,0:33:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总之，那时候不想要\NNot then, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.01,0:33:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这太没意义了\NIt doesn't make any sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.08,0:33:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不对\NNone of it fits together.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.52,0:34:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为些小事而内疚\NYou feel guilty for little things.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.66,0:34:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你能理解吗？\NCan you understand that?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.93,0:34:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你下决心会做的一切事情\NAnd what happens to everything that you make up your mind to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.33,0:34:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都有必要做吗？\NIs it necessary to do it all?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.83,0:34:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有可能同时成为另一个人吗？\NIs it possible to be one and the same person
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.74,0:34:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是说两个人…\Nat the same time? I mean, two people?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.24,0:34:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噢，上帝，真是无聊\NOh, Lord, it's so silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.64,0:34:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根本就没有理由去哭\NNo reason to start crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.98,0:34:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去拿块手帕\NI'll get a handkerchief.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.94,0:34:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天快亮了\NIt's almost morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.01,0:34:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还在下雨\NAnd it's still raining.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.02,0:35:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想象一下，不停的讲\NImagine, talking incessantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.75,0:35:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在讲，你一直在听，你一定很烦\NI've been talking and you've been listening. How boring for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.28,0:35:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的生活有什么值得你感兴趣吗？\NWhat could possibly interest you about my life?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.66,0:35:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我应该像你一样\NI should be like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.97,0:35:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道那晚我看了你的电影之后有什么想法吗？\NYou know what I thought after seeing your movie that night?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.37,0:35:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回家对着镜子，我想\NWhen I came home and looked in the mirror, I thought,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.31,0:35:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“我们很相像”\N"But we look alike."
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.51,0:35:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别误会我，你是如此完美\NDon't misunderstand me. You're more beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.68,0:35:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但在某些方面…我想如果我努力的话，可以变得和你一样\NBut somehow... I think I could change myself into you if I tried.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.79,0:35:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是说，内在的\NI mean, inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.66,0:35:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也可以成为我，就这样\NYou could be me, just like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.16,0:35:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你的灵魂太深邃，那样你会吃不消的\NBut your soul would be too big. It would stick out everywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.67,0:35:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去睡吧，否则，会在桌上睡着的\NGo to bed. Otherwise, you'll fall asleep at the table.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.02,0:36:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我得去睡了，否则我会在桌上睡着的\NI have to go to bed now or I'll fall asleep at the table.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.06,0:36:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那样肯定不舒服\NThat would be uncomfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.30,0:36:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚安\NGood night.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.28,0:39:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊丽莎白\NElisabet.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.78,0:39:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚你和我讲话了吗？\NDid you speak to me last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.78,0:40:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你到过我房间吗？\NWere you in my room?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.86,0:40:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要我给你带信吗?\NShall I take your mail, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.77,0:42:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亲爱的，我想永远这样生活下去\NMy dear, I could live like this forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.87,0:42:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沉默，过隐居的生活，无欲无求\NSilent, living a secluded life, reducing my needs,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.94,0:42:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感觉我破碎的心灵终于开始愈合了\Nfeeling my battered soul finally starting to smooth itself out.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.60,0:42:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾玛在照顾我，用最令人感动的方式宠爱我\NAlma takes care of me, spoils me in the most touching way.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.59,0:42:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我相信她很喜欢这样而且很喜欢我…\NI believe that she likes it here and that she's very fond of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.66,0:42:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或许是用一种无意识的迷惑的方式在爱我\Nperhaps even in love in an unaware and enchanting way.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.73,0:42:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何，研究她是一件很有趣的事情\NIn any case, it's very interesting studying her.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.65,0:42:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有时她为过去的罪孽哭泣\NSometimes she cries over past sins...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.75,0:42:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和陌生男孩的纵情以及随后的堕胎\Nan orgy with a strange boy and a subsequent abortion.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.82,0:42:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她声称自己的感觉\NShe claims that her perceptions
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.89,0:42:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和行为是不一致的\Ndo not correspond with her actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.97,0:48:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在看剧本\NYou're reading a play.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.89,0:48:49.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是很健康的迹象，我会告诉医生的\NThat's a healthy sign. I'll tell the doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.14,0:48:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得我们是不是很快就要走了？\NDo you think we'll leave soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.38,0:48:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有点想念城市了，你呢？\NI'm starting to miss the city. Aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.85,0:49:17.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想让我真正幸福吗？\NWould you like to make me really happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.92,0:49:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道这对你是一种牺牲，但现在我需要你的帮助\NI know it's a sacrifice, but right now I could use your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.04,0:49:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用冒什么险\NNothing dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.92,0:49:26.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想让你跟我聊聊\NI just want you to talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.92,0:49:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没什么特别的\NNothing special.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.95,0:49:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们什么都可以谈…比如说晚餐吃什么\NWe could talk about anything... what to have for dinner,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.93,0:49:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是否觉得雨后水会有点冷\Nif you think the water is cold after the rain,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.35,0:49:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不适合游泳\Nif it's too cold to go swimming.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.82,0:49:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就聊一会儿，一分钟\NJust talk for a few minutes. One minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.16,0:49:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也可以大声朗读，只要你说句话就可以了\NYou could read aloud, just say a couple of words.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.26,0:49:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在尽量控制，你还是保持沉默\NI have to try not to get angry. You remain silent.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.94,0:49:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是你的特权，但现在我需要你跟我说话\NThat's your prerogative, but now I need you to talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.11,0:50:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亲爱的，求求你，难道你一句话也不能说吗？\NDearest, please, can't you just say one word?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.31,0:50:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你会拒绝\NI knew you would refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.95,0:50:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你根本不知道我的感受\NYou can't know how I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.96,0:50:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以为伟大的艺术家，对人类有最大的怜悯…\NI thought that great artists had great compassion for people...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.96,0:50:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们的创作来源于对自身深刻的怜悯\N...that they created through a great compassion
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.90,0:50:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和需求\Nand a need to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.96,0:50:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那真蠢\NThat was stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.27,0:50:32.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你利用了我，出于不可告人的原因\NYou have used me. For what, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.21,0:50:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在你不再需要我了，便抛弃我\NNow that you don't need me anymore, you throw me away.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.88,0:50:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噢，是的，我知道这是无稽之谈…\NOh, yes, I hear how false it sounds...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.45,0:50:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“但你确实是利用我然后抛弃我”\N"You used me and then you threw me away."
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.35,0:50:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仅此而已，每句话，甚至这混账眼镜都在利用我！\NThat's how it is, every word. And then these glasses!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.99,0:50:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你伤害了我\NYou've hurt me badly.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.36,0:51:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还在背后嘲笑我\NYou've laughed at me behind my back.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.99,0:51:04.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，我看了你写给医生的信\NYes, I read the letter that you wrote to the doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.44,0:51:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，我看了，因为没有封口，我全部看了\NYes, I did, because it wasn't sealed, and I read all of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.00,0:51:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你让我说话\NYou made me talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.00,0:51:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你让我透露没向任何人说过的秘密\NYou made me talk about things I've never told anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.35,0:51:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而你，做了个成功实验，是吧？\NAnd you told. What a study, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.42,0:51:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你，你…\NYou, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.49,0:51:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说话啊！\NYou're going to talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.01,0:51:26.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你想说的话，该死的…\NIf you have something to say, goddamn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.17,0:51:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要！\NNo, don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.03,0:51:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怕了，是吧？\NThat scared you, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.02,0:52:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刹那间，你真的怕了，是不是？\NFor a second, you were really scared, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.36,0:52:03.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那种怕死的感觉，是不是?\NA real fear of death, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.46,0:52:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“艾玛疯了”，你想\N"Alma has gone crazy," you thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.17,0:52:09.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是怎样一种人？\NWhat kind of a person are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.04,0:52:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或许你在想：“我会记住这张脸\NOr maybe you thought, "I'll remember that face,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.44,0:52:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用这种音调，这种语气”\Nthat tone of voice, that expression."
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.05,0:52:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会给你些你永远无法忘怀的记忆！\NI'm going to give you something you won't forget!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.07,0:52:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在嘲笑，对吗？\NYou're laughing, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.17,0:52:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这对我来说没那么简单\NIt's not that simple for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.11,0:52:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不那么有趣\NNot so funny, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.18,0:52:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你总是有好笑的事\NBut you have always your laughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.14,0:54:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道必须这样吗？\NDoes it have to be like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.14,0:54:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别撒谎，跟我说实话\NIs it really important that you don't lie, that you tell the truth
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.15,0:54:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用一种真实的语气，聊天就那么难吗？\Ntalk with a genuine tone of voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.38,0:54:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除开谎言，托词\NCan you live without talking freely?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.15,0:54:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和漠然，你就不会别的交谈方式吗？\NLie and make excuses?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.29,0:54:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找懒惰和厌倦的理由来敷衍自己？\NIsn't it better to give yourself permission to be lazy and lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.49,0:54:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或许你展现真我会感觉好些\NPerhaps you get better if you just be the way you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.17,0:54:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，你不明白\NNo, you don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.50,0:55:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你理解不了我所说的\NYou don't understand what I'm saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.41,0:55:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是不可接近的\NYou're unapproachable.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.17,0:55:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,医生说你很健康，但我很奇怪你的疯狂\NThe doctor said you're healthy, but I wonder about your madness.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.18,0:55:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你所表现的一切让所有人信服\NYou're acting healthy so well that everyone believes you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.38,0:55:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除了我，因我知道你的堕落\NEveryone but me, because I know how rotten you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.36,0:55:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞧我都做了些什么\NLook at me behaving like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.53,0:55:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊丽莎白！\NElisabet!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.47,0:55:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊丽莎白，请原谅我\NElisabet, forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.19,0:55:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噢，上帝，我真的像个白痴\NOh, my God, I behaved like an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.19,0:55:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是来帮助你的，看我把这弄成什么样了\NI don't know what came over me. I'm here to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.54,0:55:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是那该死的信\NIt was that awful letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.38,0:55:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那让我太失望了\NI was so disappointed.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.44,0:55:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你让我谈谈我自己\NYou asked me to talk about myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.52,0:55:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我感觉很好，而且你看起来很善解人意\NIt felt so good. You seemed so kind and understanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.25,0:55:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喝了点酒，聊天的感觉太好了\NI had been drinking. It felt so good to talk about it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.21,0:55:56.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我得意忘形了，像您这样伟大的演员会听我说话\NI was flattered that a great actress like you bothered to listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.21,0:56:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同时我想那或许对你也有益处\NSomehow I thought it would be nice if it was of some use to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.57,0:56:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但那真蠢，纯粹的自我裸露\NBut it is so awful. It's sheer exhibitionism.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.41,0:56:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊丽莎白，希望你…希望你能原谅我\NElisabet, I want you to... I want you to forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.47,0:56:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我这么在乎你，你对我来说真的很重要\NI care for you so much. You mean so much to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.23,0:56:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我从你身上学到很多东西，我们不要像敌人一样反目\NI've learned so much from you. Let's not part as enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.25,0:56:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不愿意原谅我，是因为你太骄傲了\NYou don't want to forgive me because you're too proud!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.25,0:56:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不屈服，是因为你认为没这个必要\NYou don't want to give in because you don't think it's necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.55,0:56:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会…我不会…\NI won't... I won't...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:56.44,1:01:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不说话，也不听，不能理解…\N...doesn't speak, doesn't listen, can't understand...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:04.44,1:01:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊丽莎白！\NElisabet!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.45,1:01:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这意味着…不能…用来收听？\NWhat means... can't use... to make listen?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.54,1:01:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事实上…\NPractically...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:53.48,1:01:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你睡着的时候，你的脸很放松…\NWhen you sleep, your face is relaxed...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:59.49,1:02:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘴巴张开着，很丑陋\N...your mouth is swollen and ugly.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:05.49,1:02:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你额头上有一些细小皱纹\NThere's a mean wrinkle on your forehead.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:16.87,1:02:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,充满了眼泪和睡眠的气息\NYou smell of sleep and tears.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:23.65,1:02:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能看见你脖子上的脉搏\NI can see the pulse on your neck.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:27.82,1:02:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有你经常用化妆品掩饰起来的伤疤\NIt has a scar you normally cover with makeup.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:29.51,1:02:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊丽莎白\NElisabet!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:36.99,1:02:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他又在叫了\NHe's calling again.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:39.52,1:02:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去看看他到底想干什么…\NI'll find out what he wants from us...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:44.00,1:02:46.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这么远的我们独居的房子的外面\N...out here, far away here in our solitude.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:10.03,1:03:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊丽莎…\NElisa...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:13.47,1:03:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉，我吓着你了\NI'm sorry if I frightened you.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.54,1:03:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是伊丽莎白\NI'm not Elisabet.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:19.77,1:03:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没有什么需求\NI have no demands.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:22.67,1:03:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不想打扰你，你以为我不知道吗？\NI didn't want to disturb you. Don't you think I understand?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:26.55,1:03:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,医生把一切都告诉我了\NThe doctor has explained things.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:30.55,1:03:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但很难向你的小儿子解释\NBut it's hard to explain to your little boy.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:34.56,1:03:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我尽量吧\NI do the best I can.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.99,1:03:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一种很深刻的、难以抓住的东西…\NThere's something deep down, difficult to get a grip on.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:43.56,1:03:47.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你爱某个人，或者说你…\NYou love somebody, or say you do...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:48.73,1:03:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是很切实的，像言语一样\N...it's tangible, like words.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:54.07,1:03:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沃哥先生，我不是你妻子\NMr. Vogler, I'm not your wife.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:57.81,1:04:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她也爱你，你们形成了一种结合\NYou are also loved. You form a bond.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:01.58,1:04:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那给你安全，一种保持活力的机会，是不是？\NIt gives you security, a chance to endure, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:10.85,1:04:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有迷失自己，我怎么能全部说出来？\NHow can I say it all without losing myself?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:14.52,1:04:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且不让你心烦？\NWithout boring you?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:24.59,1:04:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我像以前一样爱你\NI love you as much as ever.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:36.04,1:04:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，别担心，亲爱的\NNo. Don't worry, my love.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:38.60,1:04:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们彼此拥有，我们彼此信任\NWe have each other. We trust each other.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.61,1:04:45.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们知道彼此的想法，我们互相爱着对方\NWe know each other's thoughts. We love each other.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:45.79,1:04:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是这样的，对不对？\NThat's how it is. Isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:47.61,1:04:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重要的是我们的努力，而非所取得的成绩，对吗？\NMore important is the effort. Not what we accomplish, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:54.62,1:04:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,互相看待对方\NTo see each other as children,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:56.62,1:05:00.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像是无助的孤独的痛苦的孩子一样\Ntormented and helpless, lonely children.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:01.62,1:05:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告诉你的儿子，他妈妈很快就会回来…\NTell your little boy that his mother will be back soon...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:05.62,1:05:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈病了，但她很想她的儿子\N...that Mommy has been ill, but she longs for her little boy.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:09.63,1:05:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,记得给他买一个小玩具\NRemember to buy a toy for him.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:12.63,1:05:15.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告诉他是妈妈送的礼物，别忘了\NTell him it's a present from Mommy. Don't forget.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.82,1:05:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我对你感到如此的亲切\NI have such a great tenderness for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:21.64,1:05:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,几乎快忍不住了\NIt's almost unbearable.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:25.86,1:05:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道该怎么来处理这种感觉\NI don't know what to do with my tenderness.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.64,1:05:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是靠你的亲切而活的\NI live on your tenderness.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:35.04,1:05:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊丽莎白，和我在一起好吗？你感觉好吗？\NElisabet, is it good for you with me? Is it nice for you?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.65,1:05:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道，你是一个很不错的情人\NYou're a wonderful lover. You know that.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.65,1:05:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我亲爱的！\NMy dearest!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.66,1:05:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给我镇定剂，把我扔掉\NGive me a sedative, throw me away.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:52.66,1:05:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，我不能再继续下去了…\N亲爱的…\NNo, I can't go on anymore...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:55.46,1:05:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放开我!一切太羞耻了\NMy darling...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:56.69,1:06:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave me alone! It's shameful, all of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:01.06,1:06:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放开我！\NLeave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.86,1:06:05.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我这么冷漠，这么堕落，这么无关紧要\NI'm cold and rotten and indifferent.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:05.67,1:06:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有一切都是谎言和冒充\NIt's all lies and imitation.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:17.68,1:06:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么？\NWhat have you got there?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:20.68,1:06:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你手里藏了什么？\NWhat are you hiding under your hand?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:22.68,1:06:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我看看\NLet me see.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:27.69,1:06:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你小儿子的照片，你撕掉的那张\NIt's the picture of your little boy, the one you tore up.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:33.09,1:06:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们得谈谈\NWe have to talk about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:42.70,1:06:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我，伊丽莎白\NTell me now, Elisabet.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:45.70,1:06:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么我说\NWell, then, I will.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:48.70,1:06:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是那晚的舞会，对吧？\NIt was an evening at a party, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:52.70,1:06:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夜深而嘈杂\NIt was late and rather noisy.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:56.95,1:07:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开始的时候，有人对你说…\NIn the early hours, someone said to you...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:01.02,1:07:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“伊丽莎白，你有艺术家和女人所具有的一切\N"Elisabet, you have everything as a woman and as an artist,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:04.71,1:07:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但没有慈母心。”\Nbut you lack motherliness."
Dialogue: 0,1:07:08.72,1:07:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你嘲笑是因为你觉得很荒唐…\NYou laughed because you thought it was ridiculous...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:12.72,1:07:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你还是忍不住要想他所说的话\N...but you couldn't stop thinking about what he had said.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:18.72,1:07:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你越想越担心…\NYou grew more worried...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:21.73,1:07:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因此你要求丈夫让你怀孕\N...so you let your husband make you pregnant.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:24.73,1:07:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想当一个母亲\NYou wanted to be a mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:27.73,1:07:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你发现已经成了定局时，你开始感到害怕\NWhen you knew it was definite, you became afraid,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:31.73,1:07:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,害怕负责，害怕被束缚\Nafraid of responsibility, afraid of being tied down,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:34.74,1:07:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,害怕离开剧院…\Nafraid to leave the theater...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:37.74,1:07:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,害怕痛苦，害怕死亡\N...afraid of pain, afraid of dying,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:40.74,1:07:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,害怕你日趋膨胀的身体\Nafraid of your swelling body.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:44.74,1:07:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但每时每刻\NBut all the time you acted,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:46.75,1:07:50.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你都装成是一个很幸福的母亲\Nplayed the part of the happy expectant mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.75,1:07:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每个人都说：“她从没这么漂亮过。”\NAnd everybody said, "She has never been this beautiful."
Dialogue: 0,1:07:59.76,1:08:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你几次试着打掉胎儿\NYou tried several times to get rid of the fetus.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:04.76,1:08:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是都失败了\NBut you failed.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:06.76,1:08:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当你意识到已经无可挽回时，你开始憎恨这个小孩\NWhen you knew it was inevitable, you started to hate the child
Dialogue: 0,1:08:11.76,1:08:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望是个死胎\Nand wished it would be stillborn.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:17.77,1:08:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你希望那个小孩是死的\NYou wished that the baby would be dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:22.77,1:08:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想要一个死了的小孩\NYou wanted a dead child.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:30.78,1:08:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是一个长时间也很痛苦的分娩\NIt was a long and difficult delivery.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:33.78,1:08:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你痛了好些天\NYou suffered for days.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:38.08,1:08:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孩子是用镊子取出来的\NThe baby was delivered with forceps.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:39.79,1:08:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你厌恶的看着你哭叫的孩子\NYou looked with disgust at your screaming child
Dialogue: 0,1:08:44.06,1:08:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,悄悄地说：“你能不能早点死？能不能早点死？”\Nand whispered, "Can't you die soon? Can't you die?"
Dialogue: 0,1:08:49.79,1:08:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但他活下来了\NBut he survived.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.79,1:08:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小孩一天到晚的哭叫\NThe boy screamed day and night...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:58.80,1:09:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你很讨厌他\N...and you hated him.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:01.80,1:09:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你很害怕，你感到愧疚\NYou were afraid. You felt guilty.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:08.21,1:09:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最后，亲戚和奶妈照看这个小孩\NIn the end, relatives and a nanny took care of the boy,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:12.19,1:09:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你离开病床重返剧院\Nand you could leave your sickbed and return to the theater.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:18.81,1:09:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但痛苦并没有结束\NBut the suffering wasn't over.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:23.13,1:09:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而这个小孩对却对他的母亲如此眷恋\NThe boy was seized by a massive and\Nunfathomable love for his mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:27.82,1:09:29.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你拼命的抵抗\NYou resisted desperately
Dialogue: 0,1:09:29.82,1:09:35.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为承受不起这爱\Nbecause you felt that you could not return it.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:36.21,1:09:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不断的尝试再尝试…\NYou try and try...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:38.83,1:09:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你每次和他的见面都是如此冷酷、尴尬\N...but the meetings with him are cruel and awkward.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:42.83,1:09:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你做不到\NYou can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:44.83,1:09:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你冷漠，漠不关心\NYou're cold and indifferent.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:47.83,1:09:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他看着你\NAnd he looks at you.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:51.09,1:09:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他爱你，而且他很脆弱\NHe loves you, and he's soft,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:52.84,1:09:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为他死缠你不放，你甚至想揍他一顿\Nand you want to hit him for not leaving you alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:57.84,1:10:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得他很讨厌，厚嘴唇，丑陋的身躯\NYou think he's repulsive, with his thick lips and ugly body
Dialogue: 0,1:10:01.85,1:10:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,合泪的祈求的眼睛\Nand his moist and pleading eyes.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:05.30,1:10:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你认为他很讨厌，你很害怕\NYou think he's repulsive, and you're afraid.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:10.85,1:10:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你手里藏了什么？\NWhat are you hiding under your hand?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:13.85,1:10:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我看看\NLet me see.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:19.86,1:10:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你的小儿子的照片，你撕掉的那张\NIt's the picture of your little boy, the one you tore up.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:23.86,1:10:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们得谈谈\NWe have to talk about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:35.33,1:10:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我，伊丽莎白\NTell me now, Elisabet.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:39.87,1:10:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么，我来说吧\NWell, then, I will.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:45.34,1:10:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是在一个舞会的晚上，是不是？\NIt was an evening at a party, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:47.88,1:10:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夜深而且很嘈杂\NIt was late and rather noisy.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:51.88,1:10:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开始的时候有人对你说…\NIn the early hours, someone said to you...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:55.89,1:11:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“伊丽莎白，你有艺术家和女人所具有的一切\N"Elisabet, you have everything as a woman and as an artist..."
Dialogue: 0,1:11:00.89,1:11:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你没有慈母心。”\N"...but you lack motherliness."
Dialogue: 0,1:11:06.20,1:11:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你笑了因为你觉得很荒唐…\NYou laughed because you thought it was ridiculous...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:09.90,1:11:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你还是忍不住要想他所说的话\N...but you couldn't stop thinking about what he had said.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:13.83,1:11:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你越想越担心…\NYou grew more worried...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:16.90,1:11:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因此你要求丈夫让你怀孕\N...so you let your husband make you pregnant.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:21.91,1:11:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想当一个母亲\NYou wanted to be a mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:27.15,1:11:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你发现已经成了定局时，你开始感到害怕\NWhen you knew it was definite, you became afraid...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:30.91,1:11:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,害怕负责，害怕被束缚\N...afraid of responsibility, afraid of being tied down,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:34.92,1:11:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,害怕离开剧院…\Nafraid to leave the theater...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:37.92,1:11:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,害怕痛苦，害怕死亡\N...afraid of pain, afraid of dying,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:41.20,1:11:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,害怕你日趋膨胀的身体\Nafraid of your swelling body.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.92,1:11:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但每时每刻\NBut all the time you acted,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:47.92,1:11:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你都装成是一个很幸福的母亲\Nplayed the part of the happy expectant mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:52.93,1:11:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每个人都说：“她从没这么漂亮过。”\NAnd everybody said, "She has never been this beautiful."
Dialogue: 0,1:11:58.93,1:12:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你几次想打掉这个小孩\NYou tried several times to get rid of the fetus.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:04.19,1:12:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但都失败了\NBut you failed.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:06.94,1:12:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当你知道一切都无可挽回时\NWhen you knew it was inevitable...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:10.94,1:12:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你开始憎恨这个小孩\N...you started to hate the child...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:16.20,1:12:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望是个死胎\N...and wished it would be stillborn.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:22.37,1:12:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你希望这个小孩是死的\NYou wished that the baby would be dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:28.96,1:12:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想要一个死了的小孩\NYou wanted a dead child.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:35.96,1:12:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是一个长时间也很痛苦的分娩\NIt was a long and difficult delivery.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:38.96,1:12:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你痛苦了好些天\NYou suffered for days.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:42.97,1:12:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孩子是用镊子取出来的\NThe baby was delivered with forceps.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:45.97,1:12:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你厌恶的看着你哭叫的孩子\NYou looked with disgust at your screaming child
Dialogue: 0,1:12:50.23,1:12:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,悄悄地说：“你能不能早点死？\Nand whispered, "Can't you die soon?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:53.47,1:12:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能不能早点死？”\NCan't you die?"
Dialogue: 0,1:12:54.98,1:12:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小孩一天到晚的哭叫\NThe boy screamed day and night,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:57.98,1:13:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你很讨厌他\Nand you hated him.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:00.98,1:13:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你很害怕，你感到内疚\NYou were afraid. You felt guilty.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:07.35,1:13:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最后，亲戚和奶妈照看这个小孩\NIn the end, relatives and a nanny took care of the boy...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:10.99,1:13:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你离开病床重返剧院\N...and you could leave your sickbed and return to the theater.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:16.99,1:13:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但痛苦并没有结束\NBut the suffering was not over.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:20.99,1:13:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而这个小孩对却对他的母亲如此眷恋\NThe boy was seized by a massive and\Nunfathomable love for his mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:27.70,1:13:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你拼命的抵抗\NYou resisted desperately
Dialogue: 0,1:13:29.11,1:13:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为承受不起这爱\Nbecause you felt that you could not return it.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:33.00,1:13:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不断的尝试再尝试…\NYou try and try...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:37.28,1:13:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你每次和他的见面都是如此冷酷、尴尬\N...but the meetings with him are cruel and awkward.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:40.01,1:13:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你做不到\NYou can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:43.01,1:13:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你冷漠．漠不关心\NYou're cold and indifferent.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:46.01,1:13:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他看着你\NAnd he looks at you.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:48.01,1:13:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他爱你，而且他很脆弱\NHe loves you, and he's soft,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:52.33,1:13:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为他死缠你不放，你甚至想揍他一顿\Nand you want to hit him for not leaving you alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:56.02,1:14:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得他很讨厌，厚嘴唇，丑陋的身躯\NYou think he's repulsive, with his thick lips and ugly body
Dialogue: 0,1:14:00.02,1:14:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,合泪的祈求的眼睛\Nand his moist and pleading eyes.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:03.03,1:14:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你认为他很讨厌，你很害怕\NYou think he's repulsive, and you're afraid.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:14.35,1:14:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:17.35,1:14:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是你，我的感觉和你不一样\NI'm not like you. I don't feel the same as you.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:22.53,1:14:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是艾玛护士，我到此是来帮你的\NI'm Sister Alma. I'm only here to help you.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:26.36,1:14:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是伊丽莎白．沃哥\NI'm not Elisabet Vogler.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:28.50,1:14:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你才是伊丽莎白．沃哥\NYou're Elisabet Vogler.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:30.05,1:14:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想要…\NI would like to have...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:34.54,1:14:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢…\NI love...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:38.05,1:14:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没有…\NI haven't...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:14.01,1:15:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我学过很多\NI've learned quite a lot.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:31.53,1:15:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们瞧瞧我能维持多久\NLet's see how long I can hold out.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:39.10,1:15:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我永远都不会像你，我一直在改变\NI'll never be like you. I change all the time.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:43.10,1:15:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以做你想做的事，不要打扰我\NYou can do what you want. You won't get to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:20.13,1:16:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么都不用说…对着光做检查\NSay nothing... cut a candle.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:27.13,1:16:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是现在，不，不\NNot now. No, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:31.14,1:16:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,永恒的警告，无法预料的…\NWarning and timeless. Unforeseen...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:36.59,1:16:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果注定要发生．而没有，那么…失败\NWhen it had to happen, it didn't, so... failure.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:40.56,1:16:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你呆在那里，应该是我\NYou stand there, but I should be.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:44.63,1:16:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要插嘴，不要靠近…\NNot inward, not close...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:46.15,1:16:48.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,集中精力劝告其他人\NSay collect and advise others.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:48.15,1:16:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绝望的，或许…\NDesperate, maybe...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:56.61,1:17:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我接受…是的，但最近的…\NI take... yes, but what is the closest...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:00.16,1:17:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫什么？不\NWhat is it called? No...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:04.16,1:17:07.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们，我们，我，我…\NUs, we, me, I...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:07.16,1:17:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,许多厌恶的言词\NMany words and disgust,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:10.17,1:17:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无法忍受的痛苦，恶心\Nunbearable pain, the nausea.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:45.24,1:18:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,试着听我说\NTry to listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:48.24,1:18:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟着我念\NRepeat after me...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:55.25,1:18:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没什么\NNothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:00.25,1:19:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没什么\NNothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:03.25,1:19:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，没什么\NNo, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:12.26,1:19:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没什么\NNothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:15.19,1:19:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的\NThere.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:17.26,1:19:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的\NThat's right.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:19.69,1:19:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就应该这样\NThat's how it should be.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:35.86,1:19:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剧终  谢谢观赏\N字幕由 Wendy's PaPa 重新调校时间轴

